#etcsl: line-id=B.23.8.14

:14v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) e-ne-gin₇ mu-ni-in-dib₂-be₂
#lem: ane[he]; dib[pass]

15. lu₂ zid nu-kal!-la (1:nam-uš₂-ta dirig:1)
#lem: lu[person]; zid[right]; kal[rare]; namuš[death]; dirig[make more than]
#etcsl: line-id=B.23.8.15

:15v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) nam-til₃ li#-bi₂-in-šum₂#
