21. edin-na ur-mah-e ki-tuš-a-bi-X nitalam!(|MUNUS.UŠ|)-ŋu₁₀ me#-am₃ ga-ba-ŋen
#lem: eden[back]; urmah[lion]; kituš[dwelling place]; ŋidlam[(equal ranking) spouse]; mea[where?]; ŋen[go]
#etcsl: line-id=B.23.9.21

@end proverb

